OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FMillions of drivers are embarking on
OL,7,FEaster getaway trips despite the
OL,8,Fsoaring cost of fuel with parts of the
OL,9,FNorth West congestion hotspots.
OL,11,FThe AA estimated that 21.7 million
OL,12,Fjourneys across the UK have been
OL,13,Fplanned for Thursday, 2 April.
OL,15,FThis is based on a survey of more than
OL,16,F13,000 if its members, before the
OL,17,Fconflict in the Middle East began.
OL,19,FMotoring services company the RAC
OL,20,Fpredicted it would be the busiest
OL,21,FEaster on the roads since 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
