PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FOil prices ` which have a significant
OL,7,Feffect on the cost of wholesale fuel `
OL,8,Fhave soared in response to Iran's
OL,9,Fblockade of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FThe RAC said the average price of a
OL,12,Flitre of diesel at UK forecourts on
OL,13,FWednesday was 184.2p, up 29% since the
OL,14,Fwar started on February 28.
OL,16,FAverage petrol prices have reached
OL,17,F153.7p per litre, a rise of 16% over
OL,18,Fthe same period. Most drivers are
OL,19,Fplanning to keep their Easter journeys
OL,20,Frelatively short:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FNational Highways said it will lift
OL,7,F1,500 miles of roadworks from its
OL,8,Fnetwork of motorways and major A roads
OL,9,Fin England between Thursday and Easter
OL,10,FMonday to ease journeys.
OL,12,FDrivers embarking on Easter trips to
OL,13,Fcontinental Europe are advised to save
OL,14,Fmoney by refuelling before they leave
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
