PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FAnalysis of the latest European
OL,7,FCommission data by motoring research
OL,8,Fcharity the RAC Foundation found the
OL,9,Faverage price of a litre of petrol in
OL,10,FFrance on March 23 was #1.71, some 25p
OL,11,Fmore than in the UK (#1.46 per litre).
OL,13,FA number of other European countries
OL,14,Falso had significantly higher prices
OL,15,Fthan the UK, such as the Netherlands
OL,16,F(203p per litre), Germany (180p per
OL,17,Flitre) and Belgium (#156p per litre),
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FThe figures show diesel prices were
OL,7,Falso higher on the continent, with
OL,8,Fforecourts in France (183p per litre)
OL,9,Fand the Netherlands (214p per litre)
OL,10,Fcharging 13p and 44p per litre
OL,11,Frespectively more than those in the UK
OL,12,F(170p per litre).
OL,14,FSteve Gooding, director of the RAC
OL,15,FFoundation, said: "For those driving
OL,16,Fon the continent this Easter it is a
OL,17,Fcase of out of the frying pan and into
OL,18,Fthe fire.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,F"If pump prices are high here ` and
OL,7,Findeed they are ` then in many parts
OL,8,Fof Europe they have gone through the
OL,9,Froof, including in France.
OL,11,F"It might seem counterintuitive, but
OL,12,Ffilling up at Dover rather than in
OL,13,FCalais could be the wise option."
OL,15,FManchester Airport said it was set for
OL,16,Fa record-breaking Easter weekend, with
OL,17,Fmore than 320,000 passengers expected
OL,18,Fover the holiday period.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FLiverpool John Lennon Airport was also
OL,7,Fexpected to be very busy, with more
OL,8,Fthan 64,000 passengers forecast over
OL,9,Fthe Easter Bank Holiday weekend and
OL,10,Fpassenger numbers forecast to be over
OL,11,F40% higher than the previous year
OL,13,FNorth West holidaymakers jetting off
OL,14,Fto the European Union are being warned
OL,15,Fto expect two-hour delays on arrival
OL,16,Fas countries are ramping up the
OL,17,Fdeployment of a new border system.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FThe EU's Entry Exit System involves
OL,7,Fpeople from third-party countries such
OL,8,Fas the UK having their fingerprints
OL,9,Fregistered and photograph taken to
OL,10,Fenter the Schengen Area, which
OL,11,Fconsists of 29 European countries,
OL,12,Fmainly in the EU.
OL,14,FTrade body Airports Council
OL,15,FInternational said the latest data
OL,16,Fcollected from airports across Europe
OL,17,Fshows a "continued deterioration in
OL,18,Fwaiting times at border crossing
OL,19,Fpoints".
OL,26,@yD@IOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775139066
OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FDelays are "regularly reaching up to
OL,7,Ftwo hours at peak traffic times, with
OL,8,Fsome airports reporting even longer
OL,9,Fqueues", it added.
OL,11,FEasyJet said it is preparing for its
OL,12,Fbusiest Easter getaway, with up to
OL,13,F16,000 flights from UK airports during
OL,14,Fthe two-week school break.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, thousands of Easter train
OL,17,Fjourneys will be disrupted as Network
OL,18,FRail carries out more than 270 upgrade
OL,19,Fprojects across Britain.
OL,26,@nD@LOUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
