OL,3,CRecord journeys and flights for Easter
OL,4,CGetaway
OL,6,FPassengers from Manchester, Liverpool,
OL,7,Fand the North West travelling on the
OL,8,FWest Coast Main Line (WCML) over
OL,9,FEaster weekend will be affected by
OL,10,Fmajor engineering works.
OL,12,FClosures are planned from Good Friday
OL,13,F(April 3) to Wednesday (April 8),
OL,14,Fincluding no mainline services between
OL,15,FLondon Euston and Milton Keynes, plus
OL,16,Fspecific North West issues like no
OL,17,Ftrains between Preston and Oxenholme
OL,18,Fon April 4-5.
OL,20,FTo mitigate the disruption there will
OL,21,Fbe:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
